OL,3,CFormer Tory minister Malcolm Offord
OL,4,Cnamed as new Reform leader in Scotland
OL,6,FNigel Farage has appointed a former
OL,7,FTory UK government minister as his
OL,8,Fparty's new Scottish leader.
OL,10,FThe Reform UK leader travelled to
OL,11,FScotland to announce ` as had been
OL,12,Fwidely expected ` that Malcolm Offord
OL,13,Fhas been given the job.
OL,15,FLord Offord defected to the party in
OL,16,FDecember.
OL,18,FFollowing the announcement, he said it
OL,19,Fwas a "great honour to be named today
OL,20,Fas the new leader of Reform UK
OL,21,FScotland.
