OL,3,CFormer Tory minister Malcolm Offord
OL,4,Cnamed as new Reform leader in Scotland
OL,6,F"I shall be campaigning hard between
OL,7,Fnow and May 7, to communicate a
OL,8,Fpositive vision of how we can all work
OL,9,Ftogether to make Scotland the most
OL,10,Fsuccessful part of the UK in the next
OL,11,Ften years."
OL,13,FThe Greenock-born businessman was made
OL,14,Fa life peer in 2021 by then-Prime
OL,15,FMinister Boris Johnson.
OL,17,FHe served as minister for exports from
OL,18,F2023, until the general election in
OL,19,FJuly 2024. Following his peerage, he
OL,20,Fwas made Baron Offord of Garvel.
