OL,6,FOfford continued: "We represent
OL,7,Fordinary, decent, hardworking Scots
OL,8,Fwho are fed up with mid-table
OL,9,Fmediocrity in Holyrood. Which is why
OL,10,Fwe will be fielding Reform candidates
OL,11,Fin all 73 constituencies with one sole
OL,12,Fobjective: to get Scotland back to the
OL,13,Ftop of the table."
