OL,6,F"Make no mistake, this is now a two-
OL,7,Fhorse race between Reform and the
OL,8,FSNP," he said, adding that he saw the
OL,9,Fupcoming election as a chance for
OL,10,FScots "to finally get rid of this
OL,11,Frotten SNP government, who have had
OL,12,Fplenty of time to deliver prosperity
OL,13,Ffor Scotland and have failed."
OL,15,F"Scotland needs Reform and Reform has
OL,16,Farrived in Scotland," Offord added.
OL,18,FContinuing at the conference, Farage
OL,19,Fsaid: "I think we can surprise
OL,20,Fourselves with just how many votes we
OL,21,Fmanage to garner in these elections."
