OL,6,FThe party has held off on appointing a
OL,7,Fleader until just months before the
OL,8,FMay election, despite previous
OL,9,Fassurances from deputy leader Richard
OL,10,FTice one would not be selected until
OL,11,Fafter votes were cast.
OL,13,FThe announcement comes as the UK
OL,14,FConservative leader announced that she
OL,15,Fhas sacked shadow secretary Robert
OL,16,FJenrick for plotting to defect to
OL,17,FReform.
